name: にちか
text:
──────
うまくいったってことでしょうか
trans: ────I guess that means, our performance went well?

name: 美琴
trans: Do you think it went well?

name: にちか
text:
……ど、どうでしょう
私、めちゃめちゃ…………
trans:
...I-I'm not sure.
I was really, really...

name: にちか
text: …………めっちゃめちゃ、必死だったので────
trans: Really, really, pouring my heart and soul into it───

name: にちか
text: こんなふうに、隣に立たせてもらえて…………
trans:
I feel grateful, that I was allowed to stand by
your side like this...

name: 美琴
trans:
...It's just a question of if we did it, or not.
Nothing else.

name: 美琴
text:
やれたって思える、
そういうステージだったかどうか
trans:
Whether it was a performance we can look back
and think "We did it", or wasn't.

name: プロデューサー
text:
────
『やれてたよ』なんて…………言えないな
trans:
───It's not for me to tell them whether they
"did it" or not, huh...

name: プロデューサー
text:
それでも、
俺も拍手を送りたいよ
trans: Even so, I still want to show them my applause.

name: プロデューサー
text: ────とりあえずは、よかったんだろうか
trans: ───In any case, this is a positive, right?

name: プロデューサー
trans: Although, getting MVP wasn't exactly our main goal.

name: プロデューサー
text:
彼女たちは…………
────大事なことを、大事にできたんだろうか
trans:
Whether we met our goal, depends on whether or not
the two of them... Were able to prioritize what was
most important to them for this performance.

name: にちか
text: ご覧いただいてありがとうございました……！
trans: Thank you so much for coming out to see us today...!

name: 美琴
text:
これからも良いパフォーマンスで
みんなに恩返ししていきます
trans:
We will repay this by continuing to bring you all
wonderful performances in the future.

name: にちか
text:
どうぞ、これからもシーズを
よろしくお願いします……！
trans:
Thank you once again, and please continue to
support SHHis!
